[normal]Written Evidence from Clinks [PUB0016][bold]&#xa0;
[normal]About Clinks[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Clinks is the national infrastructure organisation supporting Voluntary, Community and Social Enterprise (VCSE) Sector organisations working with offenders and their families. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Founded in 1993
[normal] and registered as a charity in 1998
[normal], w
[normal]e are a mem
[normal]bership organ
[normal]isation with over 6
[normal]00 Members including the Sector’s largest providers as well as its smallest
[normal].
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Our vision 
[normal]is of a vibrant and independent VCSE Sector working with informed and engaged communities to enable the rehabilitation of offenders.
