[normal]Question [bold]8. How realistic is it that ‘choice’ can be exercised in public service provision or should we be looking instead at greater control by users so they can ensure that public services become more responsive to changing needs?[bold]8.a How do [bold]we make sure that all citizens are able to influence public services?[bold]&#xa0;
